quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  5,24,"Nnan: \"a Musa! Nekwni ur p nkeﾃｧﾃｧem, d awez$i, skud mazal iten degs. ﾃ勃ﾃｪ, keﾃｧﾃｧ d Mass ik, nna$et. Nekwni a neqqim dagi"
  5,25,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Ay melke$, nek, siwa iman iw akked gma; ihi, Semfaﾃｴeq a$ d ugdud"
  5,26,"Inna: \"ihi, tamurt agi tepwagdel asen. Ukuﾃｩet iseggwasen ad menﾃｮaﾃｴen di lberr. Ur $webben $ef ugdud iballa$en"
  5,27,"Eﾃｪku yasen, s tidep, taqﾃｻit n sin warrac n Adem, mi ﾃｮﾃｪeggan i sin. S$uﾃｴ yiwen tepwaqbel. S$uﾃｴ wayev ur tepwaqbel ara. Inna: \"war ccekk, a k n$e$\". Inna: \"Iqebbel kan ﾃ貌bbi ﾃｮﾃｪegga s$uﾃｴ wid ipﾃｪezziben"
  5,28,"Ma ibbwev iyi d ufus ik, ad iyi ten$ev, nek, ur k id ippawev ufus iw, a k n$e$. Nek, ppagwade$ ﾃ貌bbi, Mass imavalen"
  5,29,"Nek, b$i$ a ppawiv abekkav iw, akked ubekkav ik, a ppiliv seg wat tmes. Winna d aqeﾃｮﾃｮi imednas"
  5,30,"Iaﾃ｢zem, deg iman is, ad ine$ gma s, d$a in$a t. Igwra d seg imexsuﾃｴen"
  5,31,"Iuzen ed ﾃ貌bbi tagerfa, tkeﾃｴﾃｴev akal, iwakken ad as tessenﾃ｢at amek ara i$umm loeppa n gma s. Inna: \"a ssexv iw! Ur bbwive$ ad ili$ am tgerfa yagi, ad $umme$ loeppa n gma\". Igwra d seg wid inedmen"
